problem_statement:
@Nested of Junit5 not working with @QuarkusComponentTest: Bean CDI is removed in compilation time
### Describe the bug

**When performing tests in IntelliJIdea with @Nested classes and @QuarkusComponentTest annotation then @Inject Bean CDI is removed of the context even being used in methods**

_MY CODE:_

```
@QuarkusComponentTest
@DisplayName("--- Authentication service tests ---")
public class AuthenticationServiceTest {

