problem_statement:
support var args in rest client
### Description

This works:

```
@Path("objects")
    @GET
    List<Map<String, Object>> objects(@QueryParam("id") List<Integer> id);
```

but

```
@Path("objects")
    @GET
    List<Map<String, Object>> objects(@QueryParam("id") int... id);
```

fails with `java.lang.ClassCastException: class [I cannot be cast to class [Ljava.lang.Object; ([I and [Ljava.lang.Object; are in module java.base of loader 'bootstrap')`

### Implementation ideas

_No response_

